"'''Star Wars Universe'''" is a department within the ''[[Star Wars Bust Collection]]'' magazine published in various languages by [[De Agostini]]. The department was relabeled '''Star Wars Galaxy''' in ''Star Wars Bust Collection'' 46-56, the final ten issues of the shorter-run English version released by Fanhome in the UK.

